       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID. T6BO02.
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       DATA DIVISION.
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
       01  WS-PARTNERSHIP-RULE.
           05  WS-LEGACY-BO-LIMIT   PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE 15.
       01  WS-APPLICATION.
           05  WS-PROFIT-SHARE      PIC 9(3)V99 VALUE ZERO.
           05  WS-OWNER-RESULT      PIC X VALUE 'N'.
       PROCEDURE DIVISION.
       1000-MAIN.
           ACCEPT WS-PROFIT-SHARE
           PERFORM 2100-CHECK-PROFIT-SHARE
           DISPLAY WS-OWNER-RESULT
           STOP RUN.
       2100-CHECK-PROFIT-SHARE.
           IF WS-PROFIT-SHARE > WS-LEGACY-BO-LIMIT
              MOVE 'Y' TO WS-OWNER-RESULT
           ELSE
              MOVE 'N' TO WS-OWNER-RESULT
           END-IF.
